summaries.short: Two flies experience the ups and downs of life over the course of just a few hours; a carriage horse copes with insecurity; two cats rap.
summaries.full: A pair of flies experience the highs and lows of life - finding success, failure, love and loss over the course of just a few hours. A self-conscious carriage horse is encouraged to "let it out" by a peer. Bodega-dwelling cats rap.

summaries.short: Young squirrel brothers test their survival skills on a journey to escape their overturned tree home.
summaries.full: After their home collapses, two young squirrel brothers find their survival skills tested on a journey through a tree trunk towards freedom, meeting rodent friends and foes along the way. A snake and her mouse prey face off; puppies at a pet store settle a turf war.

summaries.short: A pigeon runs into trouble when he reunites with his long-lost dad, while another struggles to encourage his son.
summaries.full: Pigeon Phil runs into trouble after he's reunited with the dad who abandoned him, while pigeon Mike struggles to encourage his son to be a seagull scout. Two turtles come to blows over the love of a mechanical frog, while a skunk learns the unfortunate truth about his date's past.
